{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If the guard likes him and tells me that she likes him-- it's a nurse, an SS nurse-- if she likes him-- and they made it all into a joke, you know, that if she likes him and she says he's a nice boy, you can keep the medicine.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if she hates him, because he's a Jewish frechling-- 'frechling' means cheeky, cheeky, good-for-nothing-- then you'll give the medicine back to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was a sort of game, you know, that he was going to issue the medicine, but Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Heller was not allowed to use it until he said, you can use it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to see this nurse in the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was my second venture outside our abschnitt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a great thing to be outside on the road and have the orientation how Auschwitz was made up, and where the crematoria were and where the sauna was, you know, and where the kommandatura was and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how-- how-- how you walked out of the gate, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What the whole procedure was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lot you knew that other people were just incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a terrific advantage that you could move about.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
